pkg2zip
------------------------------------------
Utility that decrypts PlayStation Vita pkg file and creates zip package.
Supported pkg files - main application, DLC, patch and PSM files. Also
supports PSX and PSP pkg files for use with Adrenaline.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/lusid1/pkg2zip

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/lusid1/pkg2zip/archive/refs/tags/2.6.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack pkg2zip-2.6-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./pkg2zip-2.6-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/pkg2zip-2.6-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/pkg2zip-2.6-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(pkg2zip)
  /usr/bin/pkg2zip.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/pkg2zip.README
  /usr/share/doc/pkg2zip/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/pkg2zip/README.md

